@PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check - Full
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Health Check - Liveness
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/alive
Accept: application/json

### Health Check - Readiness  
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/ready
Accept: application/json

### Translation - Translate Text
POST {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/api/translation/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello, how are you today?"
}

### Translation - Get Diagnostic Info
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/api/translation/diagnostics
Accept: application/json

### Lyrics - Get All Titles
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/api/lyrics/titles
Accept: application/json

### Lyrics - Get Random Lyrics
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/api/lyrics/random
Accept: application/json

### Lyrics - Get Specific Song
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/api/lyrics/C.R.E.A.M.
Accept: application/json

### Speech - Synthesize (POST)
POST {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/api/speech/synthesize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello, this is a test of speech synthesis.",
  "language": "en-US"
}

### Speech - Get Diagnostic Info
GET {{PoVicTranslate.Web_HostAddress}}/api/speech/diagnostics
Accept: application/json
